{"pageProps":{"data":{"news_id":"408","news_catgory":"1","hot_news":"0","news_push":"","news_on_top":"1","news_title":"中油震撼彈！董座推「電動車電池」　坦言：不轉型就等死","news_summary":"","image_path":"","news_des":null,"news_content":"<p style='box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Meiryo, &quot;Meiryo UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, sans-serif; margin: 0px 0px 25px; padding: 0px; border: none; outline: 0px; font-size: 18px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.7;'><img alt='' src='https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3820/d3820209.jpg' style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; outline: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; background: transparent; max-width: 650px; height: auto;' /></p>\n\n<div class='fb-quote fb_iframe_widget' fb-iframe-plugin-query='app_id=146858218737386&amp;container_width=1349&amp;href=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20190109%2F1351737.htm&amp;locale=zh_TW&amp;sdk=joey' fb-xfbml-state='rendered' style='box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Meiryo, &quot;Meiryo UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; outline: 0px; font-size: 18px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; display: inline-block; position: absolute; left: 122px; top: 594px;'>&nbsp;</div>\n\n<p><span style='font-size: 18px;'><b style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;'>▲戴謙接任中油董座1年多，積極推動綠能轉型計畫。</b></span></p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Meiryo, &quot;Meiryo UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, sans-serif; margin: 0px 0px 25px; padding: 0px; border: none; outline: 0px; font-size: 18px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.7;'>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Meiryo, &quot;Meiryo UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, sans-serif; margin: 0px 0px 25px; padding: 0px; border: none; outline: 0px; font-size: 18px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.7;'>「（去年）10月初中油宣布油價凍漲至年底，因為前3季賺456億元，已經高於法定盈餘120億元，中油成立目的不是要賺老百姓的錢，還有其他任務。」2週前（12月26日），中油董事長戴謙接受本刊專訪，侃侃而談這1年來的成績。</p>\n\n<div class='ad_in_news' style='box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Meiryo, &quot;Meiryo UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, sans-serif; margin: 20px auto; padding: 0px; border: none; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; width: 300px;'>&nbsp;</div>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Meiryo, &quot;Meiryo UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, sans-serif; margin: 0px 0px 25px; padding: 0px; border: none; outline: 0px; font-size: 18px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.7;'>這位70歲的老董，過去有「養鴨博士」稱號，他跨行跨很大，從畜牧、政府官員到進入教育體系，2017年11月再跳到石化產業，執掌73歲的中油，準備幫公司打造全新面貌。</p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Meiryo, &quot;Meiryo UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, sans-serif; margin: 0px 0px 25px; padding: 0px; border: none; outline: 0px; font-size: 18px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.7;'>過去中油出包風波不少，戴謙上任1年多來，也發生多次事件，被批評不懂石化專業，工會去年底還決定發動公投要罷免董事長。</p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Meiryo, &quot;Meiryo UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, sans-serif; margin: 0px 0px 25px; padding: 0px; border: none; outline: 0px; font-size: 18px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.7;'>面對外界諸多指控，戴謙了然於心，採訪當天不急著澄清，因為中油的綠能轉型計畫更為迫切，他眼神堅定地說：「我們接下來要發展中油牌電池、3年內要設1,000座充換電站，再不轉型就來不及了！」</p>\n\n<div style='box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Meiryo, &quot;Meiryo UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;'><img alt='過去以賣油為主的中油，如今準備殺入電動車市場。' src='https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3820/d3820210.jpg' style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; outline: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; background: transparent; max-width: 650px; height: auto;' /></div>\n\n<div style='box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Meiryo, &quot;Meiryo UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;'>&nbsp;</div>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Meiryo, &quot;Meiryo UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, sans-serif; margin: 0px 0px 25px; padding: 0px; border: none; outline: 0px; font-size: 18px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.7;'>近年全球氣候變遷加劇，為減少溫室氣體排放、減輕對化石燃料的依賴，多國政府與企業皆明訂減排目標，積極推廣綠色能源，行政院日前也提出「空氣污染防制行動方案」，訂出2035、2040年台灣新售機汽車全面電動化的目標。</p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Meiryo, &quot;Meiryo UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, sans-serif; margin: 0px 0px 25px; padding: 0px; border: none; outline: 0px; font-size: 18px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.7;'>但中油每年約9,000億元營收，有4成來自油品銷售，當電動車產業興起，中油將面臨3,600億元的缺口，戴謙憂心忡忡地說：「未來電動車會越來越多，油的銷量變少，這2條線會交叉在2030年，這是死亡交叉，不往新方向就只能等待沉淪。」</p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Meiryo, &quot;Meiryo UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, sans-serif; margin: 0px 0px 25px; padding: 0px; border: none; outline: 0px; font-size: 18px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.7;'>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Meiryo, &quot;Meiryo UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, sans-serif; margin: 0px 0px 25px; padding: 0px; border: none; outline: 0px; font-size: 18px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.7;'>資料來源：https://www.ettoday.net/news/20190109/1351737.htm</p>\n","keyword":"","news_order_id":"0","create_date":"2019-01-17","clk_count":"99"}},"__N_SSG":true}